{"tid":727364,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚買樓","createTime":"2018-07-03T03:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T04:16:33.000Z","uid":87785,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8114dd9d2f7c2433c0f96679bb688d8346933ac2","tid":727364,"uid":87785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩買左樓冇耐<br />\n今年年尾就結婚<br />\n連埋bonus搵35k一個月<br />\n預算婚禮淨開支17萬左右<br />\n(已包禮金及已扣除可以收返的人情）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問下各巴打當時你地結完婚買完樓仲剩幾多錢<br />\n因為而家要供樓<br />\n計完結婚後應該得幾萬蚊剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有你地覺得淨開支17萬合唔合理<br />\n你地果陣洗幾多？"},{"pid":"fa3815ee63583e0ccaae1272d7f4aaa8e0db67a5","tid":727364,"uid":44333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"睇下條女咩質素<br />\nvien等級嘅都ok嘅"},{"pid":"d6186eba395228b95fa1ec987109809bf276cc4e","tid":727364,"uid":103647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa3815ee63583e0ccaae1272d7f4aaa8e0db67a5","tid":727364,"uid":44333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"睇下條女咩質素<br />\nvien等級嘅都ok嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacad60d0303020e9be02d185b5296c70d07267b","tid":727364,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:27:37.000Z","msg":"0 all in 左"},{"pid":"fdc51466ab7222610ee69a5dcf47ddac33d80186","tid":727364,"uid":48974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29121d67ef2dc393bef8737c53552c4633cbfe9","tid":727364,"